  56,34,"washab alymyn, ma 'aezam makanatihim wjza'hm!! hum fi sidr la shwk fyh, wmwz mtrakb baedah ealaa bed, wzll dayim la yzwl, wama' jar la ynqte, wafakihat kathirat la tnfad wala tanqatie enhm, wala ymnehm minha mane, wfrsh marfueat ealaa alsrr"
  56,35,"'ina 'anshana nisa' 'ahl aljanat nshat ghyr alnash'at alty kanat fi aldnya, nshat kamilat la tuqbal alfna', fajaealnahuna abkarana, mthbbat 'iilaa azwajhn, fi snn wahdt, khlqnahn li'ashab alymyn"
